---
title: Garlic & Herb Crumbed Chicken Parmigiana with Roasted Veggie & Tomato Salad
description: Who doesn’t love a good parmigiana? Take it to new levels by adding a roasted veggie salad for a hit of freshness and bake it in a
thick gooey layer of Cheddar cheese, this tomato coated and golden crumbed chicken will definitely be the star of the evening.

